&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h1 id="solving-mathematical-problems"&gt;Solving mathematical problems&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Chaque vérité que je trouvois étant une règle qui me servoit après à en trouver d&amp;rsquo;autres [Each truth that I discovered became a rule which then served to discover other truths].&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;— René Descartes, &amp;ldquo;Discours de la Méthode&amp;rdquo;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Problem solving, from homework problems to unsolved problems, is certainly an important aspect of mathematics, though definitely &lt;strong&gt;not the only one&lt;/strong&gt;. Later in your research career, you will find that problems are mainly solved by knowledge (of &lt;strong&gt;your own field&lt;/strong&gt; and &lt;strong&gt;of other fields&lt;/strong&gt;), experience, &lt;strong&gt;patience&lt;/strong&gt; and &lt;strong&gt;hard work&lt;/strong&gt;; but for the type of problems one sees in school, college or in mathematics competitions one needs a slightly different set of problem solving skills. I do have a &lt;a href="https://terrytao.wordpress.com/books/"&gt;book on how to solve mathematical problems&lt;/a&gt; at this level; in particular, the &lt;strong&gt;first chapter&lt;/strong&gt; discusses general problem-solving strategies. There are of course several other problem-solving books, such as Polya&amp;rsquo;s classic &amp;ldquo;How to solve it&amp;rdquo;, which I myself learnt from while competing at the Mathematics Olympiads.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>There’s more to mathematics than grades and exams and methods</title><link>https://linguista.cn/person/terencetao/career-advice/orig/theres-more-to-mathematics-than-grades-and-exams-and-methods/</link><pubDate>Sun, 06 May 2007 18:49:19 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://linguista.cn/person/terencetao/career-advice/orig/theres-more-to-mathematics-than-grades-and-exams-and-methods/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://linguista.cn/person/terencetao/career-advice/zh/theres-more-to-mathematics-than-grades-and-exams-and-methods.zh/"&gt;中文版本&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;div
